4.2	Conducted regular Monitoring and evaluation of the project activities and project results and presented during PSC meetings which take place 2 times in a year, and which serves for planning development. Developed and distributed information materials and reports on the project implementation and results in order to inform wide range of population of Tajikistan, including at the regional and international levels.

